<L>__{interior joan's apartment living room day}
<A>__{a detective (melvenos) moves about, glancing at the devastation. joan, seated on a couch, addresses him: (in the b.g., helen dextra stands on her crutches near the piano, and beyond her a fingerprinter dusts for prints around the frame of the broken window.)}
<C>__{melvenos}
<D>__{you sure nothing of value has been removed from the dwelling?}
<C>__{joan}
<D>__{no, nothing. that's what's so disturbing. i mean, why would someone do something like this...?}
<C>__{melvenos}
<D>__{yeah, you have quite a nice little mess here.}
<P>__{(poking his toe}
<D>__{at some debris}
<P>__{on the floor)}
<D>__{it kinda looks like somebody doesn't like you, doesn't it?}
