<D>__{you mean lewie? he'd never do anything like this.}
<C>__{melvenos}
<P>__{(shrugs)}
<D>__{you never know.}
<A>__{there is a light knock at the partially opened front door.}
<C>__{andy }
<D>__{hello? anybody home?}
<A>__{on attractive red haired woman (antonia "andy" ellerman) stepping into the room:}
<C>__{andy}
<D>__{hi, joanie...}
<C>__{joan}
<P>__{(under her breath)}
<D>__{oh great.}
<C>__{andy}
<D>__{i just got in from hawaii and thought i'd drop by for a minute.}
<P>__{(glancing about)}
<D>__{what the heck happened in here?}
