<D>__{excuse me, it's my sister...}
<C>__{melvenos}
<P>__{(not interested)}
<D>__{uhm hmm.}
<A>__{as joan gets up and moves over to andy, he glances at his watch and exits to the bedroom.}
<C>__{joan}
<D>__{andy, this is not the most opportune time. i happen to have had a burglary in here last night...}
